       ["builtin_function_or_method"],
       true,
       "functools.cmp_to_key.__class__.__name__.__eq__('builtin_function_or_method') == True — cmp_to_key is a C builtin from _functoolsmodule.c; __class__.__name__ is 'builtin_function_or_method'; str.__eq__ returns True; new to extra146"]
